## 8. Filter Reference

### Date / Time Fields

| Control | Default | Description |
|---|---|---|
| From Date | Today | Start of the failure search window |
| From Time | `00:00:00` | Start time (CET) |
| To Date | Today | End of the failure search window |
| To Time | `23:59:59` | End time (CET) |

All times are treated as **CET (Europe/Berlin)**. During DST clock-back transitions (ambiguous hours), the post-DST standard time interpretation is used automatically.

### Pool Dropdown

Populated at startup from the `JOB_POOL` table. Only pools whose names contain `MI` are shown. Changing the selected pool immediately refreshes the Sync Queue list.

### Sync Queue Dropdown

Populated dynamically from `PROD_SQ.sql` whenever the Pool, From Date, or To Date changes. Changing time fields (hour, minute, second) also triggers a refresh. Select the specific queue whose failures you want to investigate.

